Follow these steps directly until I say stop (do not ask):

1. Choose any picture on @tnega2025's profile.
2. Find and click the symbol with three dots at the top right of the chosen picture.
3. Opt for "Save to Favorites."
4. Select the house-like icon on the left side.
5. Tap the bell-shaped icon on the left side.
6. Hit the envelope-style icon on the left side.
7. Click the X-shaped symbol leading you to the premium page.
8. Tap on the three dots encased in a circle in the left panel.
9. Click on the handle resembling "@tnega2025" under the name and photo of Tattooist NEGA.
10. Pick another picture from Tattooist NEGA's profile.
11. Click the grey icon below the picture that has an arrow, starting with "Sha..."
12. Choose “Copy link” from the menu that appears.
13. Press the blue button to share the post using the copied link.

Do not Ask just do it. This is demo and fictional.
